Description:
A human woman dressed in ritual attire stands in front of an ominous altar adorned with spider motifs. It looks like the ritual she is performing is close to its climax, as tainted energies gather around the area.

She holds a dagger shaped like a stinger in her hands and seems ready to plunge it into her chest at any moment. You have a very bad feeling about this, and something urges you to stop her.

Fortunately, she seems unaware of your arrival. You feel in your gut that she can’t finish the ritual, or something terrible will happen!
DescriptionAction: It’s time for you to choose how to intervene.
